3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper considers the optimization of power allocation and transmission rates, which are problems in systems and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper involves the transmission of information over a multiple-access channel, which is a problem in multimedia communication. 
5. cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) - The paper involves optimization problems, which are common in computational engineering, finance, and science.
